OL,3,CFire Service employer pleads guilty to
OL,4,CHaut du Mont explosion charges
OL,6,FJersey's States Employment Board - the
OL,7,Fgovernment body responsible for
OL,8,Femploying public servants - has this
OL,9,Fmorning (25 September) pleaded guilty
OL,10,Fto two Health and Safety charges.
OL,12,FThey relate to the Haut de Mont
OL,13,Fexplosion, which killed 10 islanders
OL,14,Fin December 2022.
OL,16,FThe charges the States Employment
OL,17,FBoard pled guilty to are:
