OL,3,CFire Service employer pleads guilty to
OL,4,CHaut du Mont explosion charges
OL,6,FThese fall under Article 21 (a) of the
OL,7,FHealth & Safety at Work (Jersey) Law
OL,8,F1989 - a criminal law designed to
OL,9,Fprotect workers and the public.
OL,11,FThe charges have been brought against
OL,12,Fthe board as an employer, and not
OL,13,Fagainst any individual.
OL,15,FIf proven, the board could face
OL,16,Funlimited fines.
