OL,6,FIn a statement, the Vice Chair of the
OL,7,FStates Employment Board, Deputy Malcom
OL,8,FFerey, said: "Both the States of
OL,9,FJersey Fire & Rescue Service and the
OL,10,FEmergency Services Control Centre
OL,11,F(Fire and Rescue) remain committed to
OL,12,Fstrengthening arrangements in the
OL,13,Fareas identified by the Health and
OL,14,FSafety Inspectorate's thorough
OL,15,Finvestigation.
OL,17,F"This includes training and
OL,18,Fsupervision, policies and processes,
OL,19,Fand equipment use, particularly when
OL,20,Fdealing with risks related to the
OL,21,Fsmell of gas.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
