OL,6,F"The safety of our Island community is
OL,7,Fparamount, and we will continue to
OL,8,Freduce risk, strengthen processes, and
OL,9,Fmake improvements based on our
OL,10,Flearnings from this incident and
OL,11,Fothers.
OL,13,F"While we cannot comment further until
OL,14,Fthe legal process has concluded, my
OL,15,Fsincere thoughts and prayers remain
OL,16,Fwith the families, friends, and all
OL,17,Fthose who have been affected by this
OL,18,Funprecedented and tragic event."
