OL,6,F"The States of Jersey Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService exists to make Jersey a safer
OL,8,Fcommunity. That mission continues."
OL,10,FIn a separate case earlier this year,
OL,11,FIsland Energy CEO Graeme Millar - who
OL,12,Fappeared on behalf of Jersey Gas -
OL,13,Fdenied two charges that are also
OL,14,Fcriminal offences under the Health
OL,15,FSafety at Work (Jersey) Law 1989.
OL,17,FIn a third separate case, three Island
OL,18,FEnergy employees have entered not
OL,19,Fguilty pleas to ten manslaughter
OL,20,Fcharges in connection with the
OL,21,Fincident.
